+// Threshold is a small RMS floor; real speech/room tone sits well above it.
+// ponytail: fixed threshold, not noise-floor-calibrated per mic. Ceiling: a
+// very quiet mic could false-warn; upgrade path = adaptive floor from the first
+// second of signal.
