+ * resets the quiet timer; sustained near-silence accumulates and reports true
+ * after SILENCE_HOLD_MS. Paused time can't count toward silence because the
+ * recorder skips frames while paused (nothing is fed) — reset on resume so the
+ * paused gap doesn't back-date quietSince.
